<h2 class="text-center my-4">Bony Fishes of Tubbataha Reef</h2>

<div class="text-center mb-4">
    <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTykm_zfIw3ViF7oNFWk8Q0LHcpxDVmI4fYxg&s" alt="Bony Fishes in Tubbataha Reef" class="img-fluid img-thumbnail" style="max-width: 60%; height: auto;" />
